      "rationale": "NIH MAE of 8.3% across 5 operating points. NRMSE 9.1%. All CFD predictions fall within combined expanded uncertainty band (k=2) of experimental measurements. Systematic over-prediction of 4.2% at highest flow-speed point noted and attributed to turbulence model limitations at high shear; conservative for hemolysis assessment."
